{"TopicId":202894,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Simple suggestion: using Docking Ports as crew hatches?","CreatedByName":"The Dressian Exploder","CreatedById":191542,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-06T10:16:18Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"The Dressian Exploder","CreatedById":191542,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-06T10:16:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat it says in the title. If you attach a docking port to a crewed part, it\u0027d be cool to be able to use said docking port as a crew hatch to access said part. Could also open possibilites for more \u0027airlock\u0027 style parts that you can use to disembark your crew in \u003Cem\u003Estyle\u003C/em\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Caerfinon","CreatedById":207619,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-06T11:19:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223984876\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022202894\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221622974578\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022191542\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Dressian Exploder\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, The Dressian Exploder said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nit\u0027d be cool to be able to use said docking port as a crew hatch to access said part\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can use this mod to do exactly that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u002280345\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed4039467805\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/190983-19x-all-aboard-1011-19022020-allowing-kerbals-to-board-through-docking-ports-since-2020/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:197px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"severedsolo","CreatedById":80345,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-06T11:37:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s also worth mentioning that All Aboard! is not actually limited to docking ports only. You could use it to board through any part you like with a simple Module Manager patch.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Martian Emigrant","CreatedById":158362,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-07T22:56:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223984896\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022202894\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221622978379\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022207619\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Caerfinon\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 6/6/2021 at 7:19 AM, Caerfinon said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can use this mod to do exactly that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u002280345\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed2745392174\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/190983-19x-all-aboard-1011-19022020-allowing-kerbals-to-board-through-docking-ports-since-2020/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:197px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDarn, you beat me to it. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nME\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"18Watt","CreatedById":198538,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-07T23:27:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe inflatable docking port works well for exactly this. \u00A0I think you will find a lot of support for adding that functionality to all docking ports though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPersonally, I feel that using the inflatable one is a bit more realistic- it is also an airlock. \u00A0Using a standard docking port to exit would require depressurizing the cabin every time you enter or exit.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen again, KSP is not intended to be 100% realistic, and you already have a weight penalty by adding docking ports.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnyways, the inflatable port is a current item in the stock game which can function this way.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}